    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I like the feature but I am unsure about instant API option. The library is called \"instantsearch\" but we have an option to disable the \"instant\": it was my first reaction.\n\nAny idea what could be a better naming? `searchAsYouType: true/false` was not nice :/\n\n> Along with this option we would need a submit button to be generated (as an option too), because otherwise it makes sense only on desktop\n\nHmmm, it is the goal responsibility of the searchbox? Because having a submit button means you have a wrapping `<form>` as well. Good point but not sure how to fix it :/\n",
